       8100-CONFIRMA                   SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

           MOVE "<F1> Confirmar <Esc> Cancelar"
                                       TO W-MSGERRO
           PERFORM 8500-MOSTRA-AVISO  UNTIL
                                   COB-CRT-STATUS EQUAL COB-SCR-F1 OR
                                   COB-CRT-STATUS EQUAL COB-SCR-ESC.

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
       8100-99-FIM.                    EXIT.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
       8500-MOSTRA-AVISO               SECTION.
      *----------------------------------------------------------------*

           DISPLAY S-ERRO
           ACCEPT  S-ERRO
           DISPLAY S-STATUS.

      *----------------------------------------------------------------*
       8500-99-FIM.                    EXIT.
